text: University of Al-Ma'mun (Arabic:كلية المأمون الجامعة), is an Iraqi Private college in Baghdad, Iraq. It was founded on 23 April 1990, and it is one of the oldest private universities in Iraq. ==External links== * University of Al-Ma'mun Baghdad Category:1990 establishments in Iraq Category:Educational institutions established in 1990
title: University of Al-Ma'mun
